Class LeafNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • decoder.LeafNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TreeNode

    public class LeafNode
extends java.lang.Object
implements TreeNode
    This class implement TreeNode interface. A LeafNode object has not children, but has leaf. A GroupNode could return whether it is a leaf node, get this node's symbol, and get children of this node.
